{"words":[{"word":"supply","count":3},{"word":"station","count":3},{"word":"time","count":3},{"word":"jiuyue","count":3},{"word":"area","count":2},{"word":"fog","count":2},{"word":"extra","count":2},{"word":"civilian","count":2},{"word":"into","count":2},{"word":"alone","count":2},{"word":"another","count":2},{"word":"holding","count":2},{"word":"spit","count":2},{"word":"research","count":2},{"word":"thank","count":1},{"word":"help","count":1},{"word":"tough","count":1},{"word":"fight","count":1},{"word":"leader","count":1},{"word":"though","count":1},{"word":"manpower's","count":1},{"word":"occupied","count":1},{"word":"mess","count":1},{"word":"going","count":1},{"word":"likely","count":1},{"word":"scouting","count":1},{"word":"choose","count":1},{"word":"strike","count":1},{"word":"weakest","count":1},{"word":"weather","count":1},{"word":"whining","count":1},{"word":"aix's","count":1},{"word":"mire","count":1},{"word":"kindest","count":1},{"word":"covered","count":1},{"word":"year","count":1},{"word":"plus","count":1},{"word":"frequent","count":1},{"word":"thunderstorms","count":1},{"word":"bandits","count":1},{"word":"willing","count":1},{"word":"risk","count":1},{"word":"lives","count":1},{"word":"hands","count":1},{"word":"supplies","count":1},{"word":"attacking","count":1},{"word":"settlements","count":1},{"word":"raiding","count":1},{"word":"convoys","count":1},{"word":"share","count":1},{"word":"engagements","count":1},{"word":"expect","count":1},{"word":"straight","count":1},{"word":"anyway","count":1},{"word":"consider","count":1},{"word":"reminder","count":1},{"word":"inside","count":1},{"word":"behind","count":1},{"word":"dangerous","count":1},{"word":"looks","count":1},{"word":"outside","count":1},{"word":"decide","count":1},{"word":"venture","count":1},{"word":"talk","count":1},{"word":"researcher","count":1},{"word":"academy","count":1},{"word":"sent","count":1},{"word":"investigate","count":1},{"word":"recent","count":1},{"word":"happenings","count":1},{"word":"stuff","count":1},{"word":"mean","count":1},{"word":"wait","count":1},{"word":"minute","count":1},{"word":"went","count":1},{"word":"many","count":1},{"word":"times","count":1},{"word":"told","count":1},{"word":"wandering","count":1},{"word":"ugh","count":1},{"word":"earlier","count":1},{"word":"any","count":1},{"word":"men","count":1},{"word":"spare","count":1},{"word":"exiles","count":1},{"word":"try","count":1},{"word":"run","count":1},{"word":"leave","count":1},{"word":"male","count":1},{"word":"mr","count":1},{"word":"female","count":1},{"word":"miss","count":1},{"word":"resonator","count":1},{"word":"something","count":1},{"word":"discuss","count":1},{"word":"means","count":1},{"word":"please","count":1},{"word":"current","count":1},{"word":"circumstances","count":1},{"word":"better","count":1},{"word":"bother","count":1},{"word":"find","count":1},{"word":"accompany","count":1},{"word":"investigation","count":1},{"word":"missing","count":1},{"word":"yeah","count":1},{"word":"sound","count":1},{"word":"suspicious","count":1},{"word":"boy","count":1},{"word":"sure","count":1},{"word":"i'll","count":1},{"word":"put","count":1},{"word":"good","count":1},{"word":"word","count":1},{"word":"fat","count":1},{"word":"paycheck","count":1},{"word":"helping","count":1},{"word":"government","count":1},{"word":"although","count":1},{"word":"assist","count":1},{"word":"hesitate","count":1},{"word":"stop","count":1},{"word":"trying","count":1},{"word":"anything","count":1},{"word":"irrational","count":1},{"word":"obsessed","count":1},{"word":"td","count":1},{"word":"ecoacoustics","count":1},{"word":"overexcited","count":1},{"word":"sometimes","count":1},{"word":"almost","count":1},{"word":"made","count":1},{"word":"mudman","count":1},{"word":"diving","count":1},{"word":"swamp","count":1},{"word":"data","count":1},{"word":"last","count":1},{"word":"handle","count":1},{"word":"episode","count":1},{"word":"give","count":1},{"word":"yet","count":1},{"word":"relay","count":1},{"word":"starts","count":1}],"lines":[{"text":"Thank you for your help back there. Could have been a tough fight.","quest_name":"Stygian Lacrimosa","quest_id":118000002},{"text":"Their leader was right, though. Most of our manpower's occupied with all the mess that's been going on.","quest_name":"Stygian Lacrimosa","quest_id":118000002},{"text":"They've likely been scouting our supply station for a while. Choose to strike right at our weakest.","quest_name":"Stygian Lacrimosa","quest_id":118000002},{"text":"Weather here in the Whining Aix's Mire isn't the kindest. The area is covered with fog most of the year, plus the frequent thunderstorms.","quest_name":"Stygian Lacrimosa","quest_id":118000002},{"text":"These bandits are more than willing to risk their lives just to get their hands on some extra supplies. Attacking civilian settlements, raiding convoys... We've had our share of engagements with them.","quest_name":"Stygian Lacrimosa","quest_id":118000002},{"text":"Didn't expect that they would come straight for our supply station this time.","quest_name":"Stygian Lacrimosa","quest_id":118000002},{"text":"Anyway. Just consider this as a reminder. The area inside behind us is as dangerous as it looks on the outside.","quest_name":"Stygian Lacrimosa","quest_id":118000002},{"text":"But before you decide to venture further, you should go talk to Jiuyue. He's a researcher the Academy sent here to investigate all the recent happenings. He'd know more about the stuff than we do.","quest_name":"Stygian Lacrimosa","quest_id":118000002},{"text":"What do you mean... Wait a minute, don't tell me he went into the fog alone again? How many times have I told him not to go off wandering alone? Ugh...","quest_name":"Stygian Lacrimosa","quest_id":118000002},{"text":"And you. Why didn't you tell me about this earlier?","quest_name":"Stygian Lacrimosa","quest_id":118000002},{"text":"The supply station haven't got any extra men to spare, and the Exiles might try to make another run at us. But I can't just leave a civilian like Jiuyue on his own out there.","quest_name":"Stygian Lacrimosa","quest_id":118000002},{"text":"{Male=Mr.;Female=Miss} Resonator, I... There's something I want to discuss with you.","quest_name":"Stygian Lacrimosa","quest_id":118000002},{"text":"By all means. Please. Under current circumstances, I can't think of a better way.","quest_name":"Stygian Lacrimosa","quest_id":118000002},{"text":"If it isn't too much of a bother, find Jiuyue, and accompany him in his investigation.","quest_name":"Stygian Lacrimosa","quest_id":118000002},{"text":"What is it? Are you holding out on me? Spit it out!","quest_name":"Stygian Lacrimosa","quest_id":118000002},{"text":"What is it? What am I missing?","quest_name":"Stygian Lacrimosa","quest_id":118000002},{"text":"Yeah, you sound suspicious, boy. What are you holding out on me? Spit it out!","quest_name":"Stygian Lacrimosa","quest_id":118000002},{"text":"Sure, I'll put in a good word to get you a fat paycheck for helping out with the government research!","quest_name":"Stygian Lacrimosa","quest_id":118000002},{"text":"Although you're there to assist him in his research, but don't hesitate to stop him if he's trying anything irrational.","quest_name":"Stygian Lacrimosa","quest_id":118000002},{"text":"He's obsessed with TD Ecoacoustics and can go overexcited sometimes. Almost made himself a mudman diving into a swamp for data last time. Can't handle another episode like that, no way!","quest_name":"Stygian Lacrimosa","quest_id":118000002},{"text":"Don't give up yet. We've still got some time before the relay starts!","quest_name":"Riverside Games","quest_id":125000080}]}